<plot>A look into the dark world of would be rocker Vinyl Eddie, who has chosen the path of sex, drugs and whiskey instead of focusing on his dream. The people he finds himself with are just part of his problem. Vinyl's bass guitarist, Mike calls it like it is and knows that Vinyl is a drunk who is never going to change. Drummer of the band Chris, chooses to cast a blind eye, constantly making excuses for Vinyl and his careless ways stating "It's just how he is" and "It's not that bad." After a show, a drunk Vinyl encounters a beautiful young fan named Sam and heads to her apartment with the promise of more "fun". What he finds is a moment of clarity, but is it enough to make him change? Nevertheless, he heads back to the club to have one last drink.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?014002</url></doc>
